data.name: sqlCommand3.CommandText
data.value: SELECT General.Idobra, General.Ubicacion, General.Colonia, General.Codigop, General.Solicitud, General.Fechai, General.Fechaf, General.PresupuestoZ, General.Informes, Razonsocial.RFC, Razonsocial.Domicilio, Razonsocial.Colonia AS ColRZ, Razonsocial.Codpos, Razonsocial.Encargada, Razonsocial.email, Razonsocial.Revision, Razonsocial.Pagos, Razonsocial.diar, Razonsocial.diap, Razonsocial.Facturar, Razonsocial.Telefonot, General.Paradox, General.DelOMun FROM Obra AS General INNER JOIN Razonsocial ON General.RFC = Razonsocial.RFC WHERE (General.Idobra = @IdObra) ORDER BY General.Idobra

data.name: sqlCommand6.CommandText
data.value: SELECT DISTINCT NumDoc, TipoDoc, Fecha, Recepcion, Vencimiento, IdCliente, Cliente, S, N, Agente, Anos, Semana, Importe, Saldo, Obra, Obs FROM Factura WHERE (Obra = @IdObra) AND (S <> 'X')

data.name: sqlCommand7.CommandText
data.value: SELECT FacCob.NumDoc, MAX(FacCob.NCobro) AS NCobro, MAX(FacCob.Fecha) AS Fecha, MAX(FacCob.Concepto) AS Concepto, MAX(FacCob.Anos) AS Anos, MAX(FacCob.Semana) AS Semana, SUM(FacCob.ICobrado) AS ICobrado FROM FacCob INNER JOIN Factura ON FacCob.NumDoc = Factura.NumDoc AND FacCob.Anos >= Factura.Anos WHERE (Factura.Obra = @IdObra) GROUP BY FacCob.NumDoc

data.name: sqlCommand8.CommandText
data.value: SELECT SolicitudCar.IdSolicitud, SolicitudCar.Año, SolicitudCar.Renglon, SolicitudCar.Caracteristica, SolicitudCar.Unidad, SolicitudCar.Cantidad, SolicitudCar.Ajustada, Solicitud.IdObra FROM SolicitudCar INNER JOIN Solicitud ON SolicitudCar.IdSolicitud = Solicitud.IdSolicitud AND SolicitudCar.Año = Solicitud.Año WHERE (Solicitud.IdObra = @IdObra) AND (LTRIM(SolicitudCar.Caracteristica) <> 'Área:') ORDER BY SolicitudCar.Año, SolicitudCar.IdSolicitud

data.name: sqlCommand10.CommandText
data.value: SELECT IdSolicitud, Año, Renglon, Version, IdPrecio, ISNULL(Cantidad, 0) AS Cantidad, ISNULL(Precio, 0) AS Precio, Unidad, Concepto FROM SolicitudPre AS SP WHERE (Version = @Version) AND (IdSolicitud = @IdSolicitud) AND (Año = @Año) AND (Renglon < 1000) ORDER BY Año, IdSolicitud

data.name: sqlCommand11.CommandText
data.value: SELECT IdSolicitud, Año, Renglon, Version, IdPrecio, ISNULL(Cantidad, 0) AS Cantidad, ISNULL(Precio, 0) AS Precio, Unidad, Concepto FROM SolicitudPre AS SP WHERE (Version = @Version) AND (IdSolicitud = @IdSolicitud) AND (Año = @Año) AND (Renglon >= 1000) AND (Renglon < 2000) ORDER BY Año, IdSolicitud
